My name will sound to you like Tka-a-Litan Rich-ti-a-Nick. For an impatient person like you, this is probably unnecessarily long. Therefore, call me short: Tka-Rik. If you want, you can add the words "Great Magician" to this name, but I myself do not need such solemnity.
