#phrase Rick2 9
I have no time for jokes, not at all. Everything in the world has a price, and I pay it in full. None of the Great Mages have the right to leave their island - here I am chained to the abandoned Gipat. Therefore, I need a person who can complete my assignment on another land.
#CAMERA 3
