#phrase Rick2 13
The Night of Trouble, the catastrophe that split the world, destroyed these countries: fewer traces of them remained than from the long-forgotten Juns. Only two empires survived the Night of Troubles, two eternal rivals: Kania and Khadagan.
#CAMERA 3
#ANIMATION 6
#phrase Rick2 14
Kania, where you have to go, seems to me a country where rulers do not show excessive cruelty, and their subjects feel quite free. But don't give in to the temptation to relax and don't get out of hand!
